vers.com/" target="_blank">ColourLovers</a> and more, that we&#8217;ve been using around the office to get us into the Summer mood. Behold, our tasty Summer moodboard!</p>\n<p>To us, Summer is all about enjoying the outdoors whether it’s relaxing with friends for a backyard bbq or on a warm sandy beach. Feel the beach sand between your toes, the sweetness of sorbet, the muscial harmony of a camp fire sing-a-long and nature&#8217;s undiscovered country. Summer is a gift, enjoy it!</p>\n<div class="slidedeck-link"><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/14-awesome-examples-of-summer-design-inspiration-this-week-in-deck/#SlideDeck-10883">TwiD 6/28/12 | Summer Moodboard <small>[see the SlideDeck]</small></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>What do you think? Have any other Summery design inspiration you&#8217;d like to share? Let us know in the comments!</strong></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?9d7bd4" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=4Jo81FkFuIY:NLxB8ooC4oQ:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://fe