/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8190:"<p><a href="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Featured_ImgA_Big.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8951" title="Featured_ImgA_Big" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Featured_ImgA_Big.png" alt="" width="600" height="324" /></a></p>\n<p>Bright and bold colors are now becoming common in web design. After all, these neon palettes can bring energy, friendliness, and vibrancy to a design. Take a look at the following examples and conisder incorporating this fresh style in your upcoming summer designs.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Teacake design (<a href="http://teacakedesign.com">http://teacakedesign.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://teacakedesign.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8923" title="01_teacakedesign" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/01_teacakedesign.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>2. Disqus (<a href="http://disqus.com">http://disqus.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://disqus.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8924" title="02_disqus" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/02_disqus.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>3. Love &amp; Luxe (<a href="http://loveandluxesf.com">http://loveandluxesf.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://loveandluxesf.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8925" title="03_loveluxe" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/03_loveluxe.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>4. Station Street (<a href="http://stationstreetpgh.com">http://stationstreetpgh.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://stationstreetpgh.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8926" title="04_stationstreet" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/04_stationstreet.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>5. Dearest Nature (<a href="http://dearestnature.com/blog">http://dearestnature.com/blog</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://dearestnature.com/blog"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8927" title="05_dearestnature" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/05_dearestnature.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>6. Doberman (<a href="http://doberman.se">http://doberman.se</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://doberman.se"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8928" title="06_doberman" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/06_doberman.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>7. Oliver Russell (<a href="http://oliverrussell.com">http://oliverrussell.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://oliverrussell.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8929" title="07_oliverrussell" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/07_oliverrussell.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>8. ThemeFloc (<a href="http://www.themefloc.com">http://www.themefloc.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.themefloc.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8930" title="08_themefloc" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/08_themefloc.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>9. Evoenergy UK Energy Consumption Guide (<a href="http://www.evoenergy.co.uk/uk-energy-guide">http://www.evoenergy.co.uk/uk-energy-guide</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.evoenergy.co.uk/uk-energy-guide"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8931" title="09_evoenergy" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/09_evoenergy.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>10. Purple Orange (<a href="http://peeltheorange.com">http://peeltheorange.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://peeltheorange.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8932" title="10_purpleorange" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/10_purpleorange.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>11. Salt (<a href="http://saltbarandkitchen.co.uk">http://saltbarandkitchen.co.uk</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://saltbarandkitchen.co.uk"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8933" title="11_salt" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/11_salt.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>12. KLM (<a href="http://bemyguest.klm.com">http://bemyguest.klm.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://bemyguest.klm.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8934" title="12_KLM" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/12_KLM.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>13. Crowd Track Gent (<a href="http://crowd.track.be">http://crowd.track.be</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://crowd.track.be"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8935" title="13_crowd" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/13_crowd.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>14. Into the night with Yuri (<a href="http://www.bokicabo.com/en/05">http://www.bokicabo.com/en/05</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.bokicabo.com/en/05"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8936" title="14_intothenight" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/14_intothenight.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>15. Skillshare (<a href="http://www.skillshare.com">http://www.skillshare.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.skillshare.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8937" title="15_skillshare" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/15_skillshare.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>16. Fruute (<a href="http://www.fruute.com">http://www.fruute.com</a>)</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.fruute.com"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8938" title="16_fruute" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/16_fruute.png" alt=""