<a href="http://dribbble.com/shots/408190-Quick-Setting-Toggles"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8836" title="40_btns" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/40_btns.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></div>\n<h3></h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h3>Stitchings, Glass, Fabrics and Textures</h3>\n<p><a href="http://lemon.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8837" title="41_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/41_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<h3><a href="http://meer.li/designs/air-dictate-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8838" title="42_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/42_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://www.localmind.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8839" title="43_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/43_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://www.bagigia.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8840" title="44_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/44_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://flipboard.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8841" title="45_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/45_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://dribbble.com/shots/382532-Stitches"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8842" title="46_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/46_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://dribbble.com/shots/382502-Setting"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8843" title="47_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/47_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://dribbble.com/shots/163127-Glass"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8844" title="48_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/48_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<h3><a href="http://theorydesign.ca/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8845" title="49_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/49_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></h3>\n<p><a href="http://ollysorsby.co.uk/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8846" title="50_textures" src="http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/50_textures.png" alt="" width="580" height="320" /></a></p>\n<p>Remember that inspiration for skeuomorphism isn’t limited to your computer screen. Take this opportunity to walk around and get inspiration from the world you live in.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=i5BrLthuq7s:TKUh2qqgumI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=i5BrLthuq7s:TKUh2qqgumI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=i5BrLthuq7s:TKUh2qqgumI:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?i=i5BrLthuq7s:TKUh2qqgumI:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=i5BrLthuq7s:TKUh2qqgumI:7Q72WNTAKBA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=7Q72WNTAKBA" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/digital-telepathy/~4/i5BrLthuq7s" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://www.dtelepathy.com/blog/articles/50-skeuomorphic-designs/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"http://www.dtelepathy.com/blog/articles/50-skeuomorphic-designs";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:44:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"Why the New SlideDeck 2.1 Can Make Your Life Easier";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:103:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/digital-telepathy/~3/lSsX2HiPU_s/slidedeck-2-1-update-is-officially-here";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"http://www.dtelepathy.com/blog/news-events/slidedeck-2-1-update-is-officially-here#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 19 Jun 2012 16:25:48 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"News & Events";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"SlideDeck";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://www.dtelepathy.com/?p=8759";s:7:"attribs";a:1