e awesome slideshows using your images hosted on 500px</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Current SlideDeck 2 users can update their plugin from within WordPress. Remember to install your Addons after you&#8217;ve updated the plugin, to gain access to all the new functions!</p>\n<p>We&#8217;d also like to say a huge thanks to the folks over at TechCrunch <a href="http://techcrunch.com/2012/06/18/slidedeck-2-1/" target="_blank">for their writeup</a>.</p>\n<p>Go ahead, try it out, and be sure to <a href="http://dtelepathy.zendesk.com/forums/20554402-faq" target="_blank">check out the FAQs</a>, or <a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/contact-us/">contact us</a> if you have any questions. <strong>If you don&#8217;t own SlideDeck yet, there&#8217;s never been a better time - <a href="http://slidedeck.com/pricing">buy SlideDeck today</a>.</strong></p>\n<p>We&#8217;re excited to see what you guys do with it!</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=lSsX2HiPU_s:S8_vQ1ewmoM:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=lSsX2HiPU_s:S8_vQ1ewmoM:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=lSsX2HiPU_s:S8_vQ1ewmoM:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?i=lSsX2HiPU_s:S8_vQ1ewmoM:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?a=lSsX2HiPU_s:S8_vQ1ewmoM:7Q72WNTAKBA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/digital-telepathy?d=7Q72WNTAKBA" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/digital-telepathy/~4/lSsX2HiPU_s" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1: