(19, 1, '2012-07-21 02:36:29', '2012-07-21 02:36:29', 'Welcome to our new website!\r\n\r\nHow did we do it? GiveCamp, a national event that connects technology talent with local non-profits, paired GERCF with a technical team for two and a half days of around-the-clock volunteer work, to bring our antiquated 15-year-old web site into the 21st century. This site is the result of that collaboration.\r\n\r\nKeep an eye on this page for frequent updates informing you of our latest class and workshop schedules, our library contents, and school news. Sign up for our RSS feed to be automatically updated when we add more News to Know.\r\n\r\nThanks for visiting!\r\n\r\nBarrie G. Galvin, OTR/L\r\nFounder', 'News to Know', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'letter-from-the-editor', '', '', '2012-07-21 19:13:26', '2012-07-21 19:13:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=19', 0, 'post', '', 0),
